            "title": "世界盃對美國經濟有何影響？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"世界盃對美國經濟有何影響？\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UmiX7ZsLUB7oOFvsc1kPHQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/_gjARlRRF2wl1aSm9S4e3g--~B/aD01NzYwO3c9ODY0MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://d29szjachogqwa.cloudfront.net/images/2026-06/b9605537-3dd7-4dde-aa5c-4fad2ff9a609\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">世界盃對美國經濟有何影響？</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%95%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%EF%BC%9F-021912529.html",
